              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Grace unto you, and peace, from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Grace to you, and peace, from God our Father, and the Lord Jesus Christ!</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Grace<S>5485</S> to you<S>5213</S> and<S>2532</S> peace<S>1515</S> from<S>575</S> God<S>2316</S> the<S>2257</S> Father<S>3962</S> and<S>2532</S> the Lord<S>2962</S> Jesus<S>2424</S> Christ<S>5547</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.</span></div>
