              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">We are bound to thank God always for you, brethren, as it is meet, because that your faith groweth exceedingly, and the charity of every one of you all toward each other aboundeth;</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">We ought to give thanks to God always for you, brethren, as it is meet, because increase greatly doth your faith, and abound doth the love of each one of you all, to one another;</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">We are bound<S>3784</S> to give thanks<S>2168</S> to God<S>2316</S> always<S>3842</S> for<S>4012</S> you<S>5216</S>, brethren<S>80</S>, even as<S>2531</S> it is<S>2076</S> meet<S>514</S>, for that<S>3754</S> your<S>5216</S> faith<S>4102</S> groweth exceedingly<S>5232</S>, and<S>2532</S> the love<S>26</S> of each<S>1538</S> one<S>1520</S> of you<S>5216</S> all<S>3956</S> toward<S>1519</S> one another<S>240</S> aboundeth<S>4121</S>;</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">We are bound to always give thanks to God for you, brothers,  even as it is appropriate, because your faith grows exceedingly, and the love of each and every one of you towards one another abounds;</span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
